patch_notes = "New Features:
-Patch Notes Screen has been added.
-Color Scheme across all assets has been redone to soften design language while still being readable.
-Multirail 3, Multirail 5, Rail Modulator 5, Storage V1, and Storage V2 have been added, tested and verified.
-Added a new multi-build feature that allows you to build multiple of the same building more efficiently."
